OUR STORY

ABOUT US

The CuBeanz were created by web3 passionates, long-time friends and anime lovers. As a team we decided to launch the collection as free mint to bring back the aspect of storytelling and fun of the NFT space that made us fall in love with it in the first place.

Our project emphasizes three main values of the Bushidō code: 礼-真-忠義
Respect, Honesty and Loyalty.

We are thrilled to open the doors of  the CuBeanz Temple to the world. !Yo

Read the full story
